&lt;h1 id="the-foundations-are-math-and-logic"&gt;The Foundations Are Math and Logic&lt;/h1&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Apr 5 2019&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Mathematics and logic are the basis for understanding everything else&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Naval:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Foundational things are principles, they&amp;rsquo;re algorithms, they&amp;rsquo;re deep seated logical understanding where you can defend it or attack it from any angle. And that&amp;rsquo;s why microeconomics is important because macroeconomics is a lot of memorization, a lot of macro bullshit.&lt;/p&gt;</description></item><item><title>Persuade xor Discover</title><link>https://linguage.github.io/paul_graham/essays_en/discover/</link><pubDate>Mon, 01 Jan 0001 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://linguage.github.io/paul_graham/essays_en/discover/</guid><description>&lt;p&gt;→ &lt;a href="https://linguage.github.io/paul_graham/essays_zh/discover/"&gt;Chinese Version&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
